1 Dead in Avalanche in Austria 
The new avalanche struck just miles from where rescuers were digging for victims of Europe 's worst snowslide this winter . 
Seven miles away the death toll rose to 16 from an avalanche yesterday . 
Three people were still missing .
The latest torrent of snow smashed into the town of Valzur , where two people were killed and two survivors were pulled from the snow and debris . 
